  "description": "Peek at the ItemStack NBT!",
  "body": "<center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This mod brings the staple QOL of memeversions into 1.7 in form of NBT Tooltips with crude wrapping.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/528472643221848085/847431796181696562/unknown.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"437\" height=\"142\" /></p>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\">ItemStack links to the chat (if the mod is also installed serverside due to engine limitations). To link the item, press CTRL+T while hovering over an item inside any inventory GUI.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/528472643221848085/883903011678732288/unknown.png\" width=\"437\" height=\"82\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/poop-person/991e80f390384bbeef09d208bff208f4\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/gist/poop-person/991e80f390384bbeef09d208bff208f4/raw/a9ef83add84a70f2202896c2d81117ff7b169be1/poop-badge.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"62\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n</center>",
